narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great reading and a fantastic group of students to discuss with.

I would not recommend this class. The assignments were good but Professor Hartman was a terrible teacher. She spoke to us as if we were all in the fourth grade. She mostly assigned her NYT articles for reading, as if she had won a Pulitzer. And her feedback just wasn't substantive enough for a writing-intensive seminar. She'd make small wording/grammar changes and then act as if you had submitted a truly pitiful piece of work. Maybe I have an axe to grind, but I found her teaching style to be objectively poor and self-congratulatory. Do not take this class.
